name: R'EVOL #002 - THE KING
description:
The R'EVOL project. 
A new series of insane characters inspired by the work of KidEight, newly created by upcoming artist Kingsbridge.


MEET #002 - THE KING, The Ruler of way too much.

STORY:
"Ah yes, The King. Infamous ruler of three countries, 16 islands, and at least two fashion brands. He tells everyone (even when they didn’t ask) that he was only kicked out of heaven because God himself got jealous of his “skill, charm, and overall talent”.

It’s hard to confirm whether this is actually true, but The King sure acts like it is. Armed with several magical artifacts he rules with an iron fist, at least when he’s not blackout drunk.

So far he had a total of 8 portraits made of him. The 6th one, stolen by The Collector, is pictured above."


Buy his unique PORTRAIT today!
Thank you for supporting young and upcoming artists :)
